Donovan Leitch (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donovan_Leitch_(actor) 0 Donovan Jerome Leitch Jr (born 16 August 1967) is an English-born American actor, singer and former model. He is the son of the singer-songwriter Donovan and the brother of actress Ione Skye. He was member of the hard rock band Camp Freddy, and was a founding member of neo-glam group Nancy Boy along with Jason Nesmith, the son of Michael Nesmith of The Monkees.
